   T
</CO>
<IN>
TENDER OFFERS, MERGERS, ACQUISITIONS (TNM)
</IN>
<LP>
   American Telephone &amp; Telegraph Co. has sold part of its
shareholding in Cie. Industriali Riunite S.p.A. to Sprind
Gestione S.p.A., another company controlled by the Italian
financier Carlo De Benedetti.
   Angelo Abbondio, chairman of Sprind Gestione, said in an
